        "text_jqjUTm": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Welcome to the Clarity Theme documentation. This guide covers the usage and customization of the theme’s advanced sections, including Parallax, Media Slider, Animated Image with Text, Timeline, and more.</p>"
          }
        },
        "heading_8PRk4y": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Table of Contents",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_j4Dgjw": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<ul><li><strong>Introduction</strong></li><li><strong>Section Overview</strong></li><li><strong>How  to Add & Configure Sections</strong></li><li><strong>Best Practice</strong></li><li><strong>Support</strong></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>INTRODUCTION</strong></p><p>Clarity Theme v1.0 offers a range of interactive and visually engaging sections to help you build a unique storefront. This documentation explains how to use and customize each section.</p><h3><strong>Section Overview</strong></h3><h4><strong>Mega Menu</strong></h4><p><strong>Description:</strong><br/>We have options to select a menu in Header section and in blocks of header section we have Mega Tab block.</p><p><strong>How to Use:</strong></p><ul><li>In Header section we have Option <strong>Desktop Menu Type</strong> under <strong>Menu Style</strong>, we should select <strong>Mega Menu</strong> from there.</li><li>Then we need to add <strong>Mega Tab</strong> block, there we have option to select <strong>collections </strong> and a text field named <strong>Link Name.</strong></li><li>In <strong>Link Name</strong> we need to add value of the menu item we want to target and then select collections, this way all the selected collections will be displayed under targeted menu item.</li></ul><h4><strong>Parallax Section</strong></h4><p><strong>Description:</strong></p><p>Create immersive scrolling effects by adding background images that move at a different speed than foreground content.<br/><br/><strong>How to Use:</strong></p><ul><li>Add the Parallax section from the theme editor.</li><li>Upload your background image and adjust speed settings.</li><li>Customize overlay text, colors, and call-to-action buttons.</li></ul><h4><strong>Media Slider</strong></h4><p><strong>Description:</strong><br/>Showcase multiple images or videos in a responsive slider.</p><p><strong>How to Use:</strong></p><ul><li>Add the Media Slider section.</li><li>Upload images or videos.</li><li>Set transition effects, autoplay, and navigation options.</li></ul><p></p><h4><strong>Animated Image with Text</strong></h4><p><strong>Description:</strong><br/>Combine animated images (GIFs or SVGs) with customizable text blocks for dynamic storytelling.</p><p><strong>How to Use:</strong></p><ul><li>Add the Animated Image with Text section.</li><li>Upload your animated image.</li><li>Enter headline, description, and choose animation style.</li><li>To put animate svgs on text wrap text with round bracket followed by asterisk like: (*text*) then we have a liquid code field below text field. Just paste the svg code there.</li></ul><p></p><h4><strong>Timeline</strong></h4><p><strong>Description:</strong><br/>Display a chronological sequence of events, milestones, or brand history.</p><p><strong>How to Use:</strong></p><ul><li>Add the Timeline section.</li><li>Add timeline items with dates, titles, and descriptions.</li><li>Customize colors and layout orientation.</li></ul><p></p><h4><strong>How to Add & Configure Sections</strong></h4><ol><li><strong>Open Theme Editor:</strong><br/>Go to Shopify Admin → Online Store → Themes → Customize.</li><li><strong>Add Section:</strong><br/>Click \"Add section\" in the sidebar and select your desired section (e.g., Parallax, Media Slider).</li><li><strong>Configure Content:</strong><br/>Use the settings panel to upload images, enter text, and adjust design options.</li><li><strong>Reorder Sections:</strong><br/>Drag and drop sections to change their order on the page.</li><li><strong>Save & Preview:</strong><br/>Click \"Save\" and preview your changes. </li></ol><h4><strong>Best Practices</strong></h4><ul><li>Use high-quality images for parallax and sliders.</li><li>Keep text concise and engaging.</li><li>Test animations and sliders on mobile devices.</li><li>Use timeline to highlight key brand moments or product launches.</li></ul>"
          }
